//toast in java:(just like in email in message save as dreafts)
//A toast provides simple feedback about an operation in a small popup
///It only fills the amount of space required for the message 
//the current activity remains visible and interactive. Toasts automatically disappear after a timeout.
  
//code
Toast.makeText(this, "You cannot have less than 1 coffee", Toast.LENGTH_SHORT).show();    
